===Het===
====Initial dialogue====
* '''Het:''' Amascut! She's always been a monster, but she's doing things now I never believed her to be capable of! Had I not let my guard down, she'd surely be regretting her choices by now.
* '''Het:''' I guess we're lucky you came along when you did, my friend. I think you might have just given us a fighting chance!
* '''Player:''' I'm glad to have helped, but it's not over yet.
* '''Het:''' Indeed. Were I not still weak, I would gladly deal with her myself, but I fear you will have to face Amascut without me.
* {{tcond|If the other Avatars of Tumeken have not been freed yet:}}
** '''Het:''' You'll find her on the level below. If you can free the others, we should be able to open the way for you.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If all of the other Avatars of Tumeken have been freed:}}
** '''Het:''' You'll find her on the level below. We have managed to open the way for you. Go now, and show her the error of her ways!
** {{tact|end}}

====Subsequent dialogue====
* {{tcond|If the other Avatars of Tumeken have not been freed yet:}}
** '''Het:''' My friend, Amascut has heavily weakened me, but I know you can do what is needed. If you can free the others, we should be able to open the way to the level below.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If all of the other Avatars of Tumeken have been freed:}}
** '''Het:''' We have opened the way for you, my friend. Any other day, I would have joined you in the fight against Amascut, but this one is up to you. Go now, and show her the error of her ways!
** {{tact|end}}

===Scabaras===
====Initial dialogue====
* '''Player:''' Are you okay?
* {{tcond|If the other Avatars of Tumeken have not been freed yet:}}
** '''Scabaras:''' The silence... it's so loud! Free the others! Free them and we can help. Now please... go!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If all of the other Avatars of Tumeken have been freed:}}
** '''Scabaras:''' We... opened the way. Now... go. Stop her! Please!
** {{tact|end}}

====Subsequent dialogue====
* {{tcond|If the other Avatars of Tumeken have not been freed yet:}}
** '''Scabaras:''' The silence... it's so loud! Free the others! Free them and we can help. Now please... go!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If all of the other Avatars of Tumeken have been freed:}}
** '''Scabaras:''' We... opened the way. Now... go. Stop her! Please!
** {{tact|end}}

==The Wardens==
===Talking to Amascut===
* '''Amascut:''' You! I should have known this would be your doing!
* '''Player:''' It's over, Amascut! Your plan has failed.
* '''Amascut:''' My plan has only just begun! Even with this setback, those pathetic fragments of my father have still given me ample power. My strength is absolute!
* '''Player:''' Maybe, but it doesn't matter. I've stopped every one of your schemes so far, and I'll stop the next one as well.
* '''Amascut:''' Really? You think you're leaving this place alive? I can promise you that won't be the case! My father's weapons have given me his power, and now they'll finally rid me of you!
* {{tselect|Are you ready for the final challenge?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** {{qact|Amascut activates the obelisk and teleports away.}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** {{tact|end}}

==Finishing up==
===Talking to Osmumten===
* {{tbox|As you approach the spirit, you hear a voice echoing in your head.}}
* '''Spirit:''' {{Colour|#000080|You. You fought against the Devourer. Her influence here has been lessened as a result. You are to be commended for your strength.}}
* '''Player:''' I take it you're Osmumten?
* '''Osmumten:''' {{Colour|#000080|Once, but who I was in life means nothing. Vengeance is all that matters now. The Devourer may be gone, but my home has been corrupted. This corruption must be destroyed.}}
* '''Player:''' Can I help?
* '''Osmumten:''' {{Colour|#000080|You can. Take your prize and leave, but when you are ready, return here. The Devourer's thralls will soon be back. You must fight them.}}
* '''Player:''' I'll do what I can.
* '''Osmumten:''' {{Colour|#000080|We shall see if it is enough.}}
* {{tselect|Are you ready to leave the Tombs of Amascut?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** {{tact|Player gets teleported to the [[Tombs of Amascut]] lobby.}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** {{tact|end}}

