{{tcond|If the player has a full inventory and the [[Antique lamp (Into the Tombs)|Antique lamp]] wasn’t used yet:}}
** '''Maisa:''' You're back! I have a little something for you, but you don't seem to have room for it. Come back when you do.
** {{tact|end}}
